column1: This file is derived from the following two files: "Microbiome homeostasis on rice leaves is regulated by a precursor molecule of lignin biosynthesis" (doi: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-023-44335-3) supplimentary data 1 and

"Recovery of metagenome-assembled genomes from the phyllosphere of 110 rice genotypes" (doi: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-022-01320-7) supplimentary data 2. As it is from someone else work I can't upload it to my github. Refer the file and follow my codes to get this data.
